<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA43">
<l>avaya meṉaniṉaintu vantacurar pālē</l>
<l>navaiyai naḷirvippāṉ ṟaṉṉai kavaiyiṉ</l>
<l>maṉattuyara vaittiruntu vāḻttātārk kuṇṭō</l>
<l>maṉattuyarai māykkum vakai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Him] who, on behalf of the gods come thinking [him to be] the refuge,</l>
<l>causes evil to tremble, is there, for those who do not keep seating [and]</l>
<l>praising him, for [their] unbifurcated minds to be elevated,</l>
<l>a way to destroy [their] minds’ misery?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
